          ],
          "caption": "",
          "uid": "b0d915piw",
          "mediaHeight": 300,
          "hideCaptions": false,
          "spacing": "tight"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "We needed a format where the user wanted to engage before they even knew a product was waiting on the other side. Holi — tactile, playful, built around surprise and colour was the perfect wrapper for that idea. The festival didn't just set the visual tone, it justified the interaction model.",
          "uid": "bpmh0l0nh"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b09r54bwr",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "These two campaigns one for Valentine's Day, one for Holi were our attempt at doing it differently. Same goal across both: surface a relevant product to the right user at the right cultural moment. The cross-sell items were identical across campaigns, but the interaction pattern was designed fresh each time to match the mood of the festival."
        },
        {
          "uid": "bbh511tsd",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md",
          "spaceAfter": 50,
          "spaceBefore": 50
        },
        {
          "uid": "b6ofon1ap",
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "WHY THIS APProach?"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b53yfaw10",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Festivals put users in a different headspace. They're generous, they're playful, they're open. We used that window intentionally — wrapping a product recommendation inside something people actually wanted to interact with. The festival didn't just set the visual tone, it justified the interaction. That's what made these campaigns feel earned rather than interrupting."
        },
        {
