        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Impact",
          "uid": "bgfj397g8"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "The point was not to make a campaign banner look festive. It was to turn a product recommendation into a small act of discovery — one where surprise came before the sell.",
          "uid": "bwlhvxcxi"
        },
