    {
      "id": "reflection",
      "label": "Reflection",
      "indexLabel": "Reflections",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Reflection",
          "uid": "bhb7th0np"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Growth experiments sat in a useful space between product design and campaign design. They had to work like product surfaces, but feel timed, playful, and worth opening.",
          "uid": "bz7359jf7"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "The strongest version of these moments came when the campaign mechanic carried the product idea instead of sitting on top of it.",
          "uid": "b1fzvwwga"
        },
        {
